# SCSS Standards

## Block SCSS Structure

### Required Pattern

```scss
// ✅ GOOD
.il_block.il_block-name {
  padding-top: var(--b-space-top-ld);
  padding-bottom: var(--b-space-bottom-ld);
  padding-left: var(--b-space-left-ld);
  padding-right: var(--b-space-right-ld);
  
  @include limbo-max {
    padding-top: var(--b-space-top-mt);
    padding-bottom: var(--b-space-bottom-mt);
    padding-left: var(--b-space-left-mt);
    padding-right: var(--b-space-right-mt);
  }
  
  .il_block-name_inner {
    // Inner container styles
  }
}

// ❌ BAD - Missing responsive breakpoints
.il_block.il_block-name {
  padding: 2rem;
}
```

## CSS Variables Pattern

### Spacing Variables

```scss
// ✅ GOOD - Use CSS variables for ACF-controlled values
padding-top: var(--b-block-space-top-ld);
@include limbo-max {
  padding-top: var(--b-block-space-top-mt);
}

// ❌ BAD - Hardcoded values
padding-top: 4rem;
```

### Naming Convention

- Block spacing: `--b-block-name-space-{side}-{breakpoint}`
- Inner section: `--b-inner-sec-space-{side}-{breakpoint}`
- Intro spacing: `--b-intro-space-{side}-{breakpoint}`
- Background elements: `--bg-e-{property}-{breakpoint}`

## Responsive Breakpoints

```scss
// ✅ GOOD - Always include mobile styles
.il_block.il_block-name {
  // Desktop styles (ld)
  font-size: 2rem;
  
  @include limbo-max {
    // Mobile/tablet styles (mt)
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}

// ❌ BAD - Missing mobile breakpoint
.il_block.il_block-name {
  font-size: 2rem;
}
```

## Class Naming

```scss
// ✅ GOOD - Consistent BEM-like pattern
.il_block.il_block-name {
  &_inner {
    // Inner container
  }
  &_element {
    // Block element
  }
}

// ❌ BAD - Inconsistent naming
.block {
  .inner {}
  .element {}
}
```

## Image Responsive Pattern

```scss
// ✅ GOOD - Hide/show desktop/mobile images
.desk_img {
  display: block;
  @include limbo-max {
    display: none;
  }
}

.mob_img {
  display: none;
  @include limbo-max {
    display: block;
  }
}

.hide_desk_img_mob {
  @include limbo-max {
    display: none;
  }
}

// ❌ BAD - Single image without responsive handling
.block-image {
  width: 100%;
}
```

## Import Structure

```scss
// ✅ GOOD - Import in frontend.scss
@import 'blocks/your-block-name';

// ❌ BAD - Importing in wrong file or missing import
```
